			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>You didn't say which graphics chipset your HP came with. Most of them come with Geforce FX, which is compatible with Everquest. Some don't, though. However, if your HP does not have a Geforce FX, stop reading and tell us what you have. 
<br />

<br />
Go to Control Panel - Display - Settings - Advanced - Adapter.
<br />

<br />
Write down the &quot;Adapter Type&quot; and post it here.
<br />

<br />
Then click on Properties - Driver and tell us the Driver Version and Driver Date.</span></td>
