				<td colspan="2"><span>Okay, your drivers are really old. The most recent drivers for your card are dated 4-1-2004. Go here and download the latest driver package: <a target="_new" href="http://www.nvidia.com/object/winxp_2k_56.72">nVidia Forceware 56.72</a>.
<br />

<br />
Before you install it, make sure to remove the old drivers by browsing to the Start Menu &gt; Windows Control Panel &gt; Add/Remove Programs and search for &quot;NVIDIA Windows Display Drivers&quot; or &quot;NVIDIA Display Drivers&quot; and selecting &quot;remove.&quot;
<br />

<br />
That's a problem sometimes... even when your computer is brand new you have no idea how many weeks it was sitting on a shelf or in a warehouse before you bought it...</span></td>
