				<td colspan="2"><span>Heads up !
<br />

<br />
You cant use the general drivers for the mobile GPUs.
<br />

<br />
Nvidia doesnt offer drivers for notebook-graphic-cards - you need to check the HP-homepage for an driver-update
<br />

<br />
Quote:
<br />
<i>ForceWare Release 55 graphics driver is the graphics driver for all NVIDIA graphics processing units (GPUs). <u>GeForce2 Go, GeForce4 Go and GeForce FX Go mobile processors are not supported in this driver. Please contact the notebook's manufacturer for graphics drivers for your notebook PC</u></i> </span></td>
			</tr><tr>
